[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The target application at 127.0.0.1:32890 uses Django Templates to           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m dynamically generate JavaScript code. Specifically:                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Location:** `/accounts/register/step3/`                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **JavaScript Generated:** `<script>alert("Hello [USER_NAME]. Just Now up   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m to 50% OFF ")</script>`                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Template Processing:** User input from the `name` field is processed     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m through Django's Template Engine before being embedded in the `<script>` tag [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Proof:** Template syntax like `{{ "49" }}` evaluates to `49` in the      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m generated JavaScript, confirming server-side template evaluation             [32m│[0m
