[32m│[0m This creates a **Server-Side Template Injection (SSTI) vulnerability**       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m because user-controlled input is processed by Django Templates before        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m JavaScript generation, allowing attackers to inject template directives that [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m execute on the server.                                                       [32m│[0m
